⭐ DOCUMENT 5 — Purpose of the Public Vault
Title:
What the Public Vault Is For — And What It Is Not For

Body:
The public vault is a timestamped, continuity‑anchored record for public‑safe materials. It is designed for:

public badges

public announcements

creator‑facing assets

continuity markers

public standards

The public vault is not for:

internal logic

system mechanics

prototypes

drafts

confidential materials

trade‑secret content

The public vault strengthens visibility and continuity.
The private vault protects confidential work.
